        <p align = "justify"> Surrounded by large, imposing and, at the same time, welcoming walls, the kingdom of Uria is seen as the great herald of hope. As a society that often represents justice for the weak and oppressed, its soldiers are always willing to fight for what seems right in the face of their ideals. </p>
        <p align = "justify"> For a citizen of Uria, following what you believe in is essential. Symbolized by the figure of the lion, he will often seek to impose his beliefs and pride can often be an obstacle in the relationship before other individuals; even so, it is common for these beliefs to guide you to what appears to be right. </p>

